2026-06-14 version 1.5.3
* Docs-only release: standardize the README to the canonical skeleton and unify
  the status badges and CI workflow name. No code or dependency changes.

2026-06-13 version 1.5.2
* Bump default/dev Clojure 1.12.0 to 1.12.5 (latest patch). Provided scope, so
  no consumer impact; the 1.12 test profile now runs on the current release.

2026-06-10 version 1.5.1
* Default to Clojure 1.12.0; test across Clojure 1.10/1.11/1.12.
* Enable *warn-on-reflection*; the build is reflection-clean and CI enforces it.
* Realign the deprecated single-segment digest namespace with clj-commons.digest.
* Document the 1.5.0 UTF-8 string-encoding behavior change.

2026-06-09 version 1.5.0
* Publish maintenance fork as net.clojars.savya/digest.
* Add raw byte and base64 digest output helpers.
* Add HMAC helpers and constant-time byte-array comparison.
* Add file digest convenience helpers and algorithm metadata helpers.
* BEHAVIOR CHANGE: strings are now encoded as UTF-8 by default instead of the
  JVM default charset. On a non-UTF-8 JVM this changes the digest of non-ASCII
  strings versus 1.4.x. Pass an explicit encoding to reproduce old output.

2021-10-11 version 1.4.93
* The digest namespace has moved to clj-commons.digest. The old one is deprecated.

2018-03-25 version 1.4.10
* Test using for public domain data (issue #11)

2018-03-25 version 1.4.8
* Minor fixes (@laurio in PR #8)

2018-03-18 version 1.4.7
* Minor simplifications, fix typo.
* Clojure 1.9.0

